    <!-- About -->
    <string name="text_use">Touchpad mode:\nUse your phone like a touchpad of a notebook. You can choose single- or multitouch mode, too.\n\nPresenter mode:\nYour phone can be a platform and software independent remote control.\nYou can configure the several controllers and can run system commands in addition.\n\nGesture presenter:\nBoth in touchpad and presenter mode can be able to step forward by a gentle hand gesture to left. It can be turned on from menu.\n\nParticular settings can be found at menu.\n\nServer side software can be downloaded:\n--Kérnék egy itk-s címet, ha lehet--</string>
